{"title":"脚手架上的诗","authors":["聂鑫森"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚手架上的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南株洲　聂鑫森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一节节钢管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的手上伸延。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵和横的座标线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮当地响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个大大小小的方格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"规划着淡青色的云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个生活的切面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳亮晶晶地微笑在格子的上端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在格子间腾跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲洗一张偌大的照片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个如历史一样凝重的结头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经拧紧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它掌管的那个空间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳定着创造的狂欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多层次的追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正清晰地显现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在纵横的座标线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是一个座标点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标示着我们的位置，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅仅是为了一栋大楼的崛起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是宣告新的年代的开端。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}